properties.areaDesc: Coastal Waters from Point Reyes to Pigeon Point California out to 10 nm
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 20 at 8:28AM PST until January 21 at 9:00PM PST by NWS San Francisco CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...South winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and seas
8 to 10 feet at 18 seconds expected.

* WHERE...Coastal Waters from Point Reyes to Pigeon Point
California out to 10 nm.

* WHEN...From 3 PM this afternoon to 9 PM PST Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 3 PM THIS AFTERNOON TO 9 PM PST TUESDAY
